data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom house in the Traditions neighborhood has tons of space and is a true masterpiece. This home is within walking distance of the pool and clubhouse. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line and brand new appliances including a gas stove, sleek countertops, and ample storage space.  But wait, there's more! This home offers a fantastic finished basement that adds a whole new dimension to the property. The basement provides additional living space, perfect for a home theater, game room, or even a home gym. It also has it's own bedroom and bathroom. The possibilities are endless! A good sized fenced backyard is just waiting for you to make the backyard your own. Contact us for your private showing - this is not one you want to miss!!
